title: Gazing at the You I Love, Fire Emblem Engage
description: Negomu-sensei brings us a touching story featuring Alear and Veyle's first intimate moment! Witness Veyle's adorable shyness as she nervously accepts Alear's kiss! Every time Alear teases her, Veyle lets out the sweetest sounds of surprise and delight. Yearning to feel even closer to Alear, what will Veyle do next...?
